## 7. What Not to Build

Do not build around these old ideas:

* full-history prompting
* top-level booleans like `speech_change` and `consciousness_change`
* `laterality` as a single string
* concern estimation from latest message only
* caregiver summary as an afterthought outside orchestration

If any of these exist in the current codebase, refactor away from them.
If they do not exist yet, do not introduce them.

