## 13. Exact Pipeline Flow to Create

Create or refactor the pipeline so it follows this flow exactly:

```text
new_user_input
  -> update CaseState with extracted updates
  -> recompute missing fields
  -> if key field missing: ask one follow-up question
  -> else estimate concern level
  -> map concern to action
  -> detect hesitation with minimal recent context only
  -> build user-facing message
  -> build caregiver output
  -> return updated CaseState
```

This is the required structured pipeline.

