## 16. Caregiver Output Wiring

Caregiver output is complete only if all four layers are updated:

1. `CaseState` has `caregiver_output`
2. `app.yaml` has `enable_caregiver_output`
3. `pipeline/orchestrator.py` calls `summary_generator`
4. output contract exposes caregiver output

If any one of these four is missing, caregiver output is not fully implemented.

